" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 560px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Blepharitis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 540px; height: 371px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Blepharitis is associated with crusting of the eyelashes, thickening of the eyelids, telangiectatic vessels along the lid margins, and plugging of the meibomian glands.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
