" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Prevalence of adenomatous colonic polyps increases with age",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 415px; height: 256px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Adenomatous colonic polyps are found in about 25 percent of people by the age of 50; the prevalence continues to increase with increasing age.",
